johar.interfaceinterpreter.star
Interface CommandControllerBase

All Known Implementing Classes:
CommandController
public interface CommandControllerBase

This interface interacts with the Widgets; It performs any action required by the user, while handling all events generated by the Widgets; It interacts with the Gem via GemSetting and the Idf to serve requests raised from the Widgets.
